snippet.title: Tall Poppy | Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Tall Poppy is a short-but-sweet, funhouse-horror adventure about a man on a quest to retrieve his wife's purse she mistakenly forgets in the local cemetery. Using your trusty dashboard flashlight, in the middle of the night, *gulp*, explore the church grounds while evading a sinister "presence!"

Pick up your copy of Tall Poppy
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1814770/Tall_Poppy/
Humble Bundle: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/tall-poppy
Itch: https://attainableentertainment.itch.io/tall-poppy
GameJolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/TallPoppy/381734
